# Placeholder for Linux binary
# The actual MeowthBridge will be placed here during the build process
# by GitHub Actions or manual compilation.

To build manually:
  dotnet publish src/MeowthBridge -c Release -r linux-x64 --self-contained -p:PublishSingleFile=true -o src/meowth/binaries/linux
  chmod +x src/meowth/binaries/linux/MeowthBridge
